.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-LOCAL-BALANCE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-local-balance \- show total local balance across all channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-local-balance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the sum of local balances and total capacity across all active channels.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"local_balance_msat":N, "local_balance_sat":N, "total_capacity_msat":N, "active_channels":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-remote-balance (1),
.BR lightning-channel-balance-ratio (1)
